# Capstone Lab - XSS to Reverse Shell (WordPress)

## Objective

The goal of this lab was to:

* Exploit a Stored XSS vulnerability to create a new administrator account
* Upload a malicious WordPress plugin to gain code execution
* Upgrade a web shell to a reverse shell
* Capture the flag from the target system

