## Step 1 - Stored XSS Exploitation

A Stored XSS payload was injected via the User-Agent header:

curl -s http://offsecwp/ -H "User-Agent: <script>eval(String.fromCharCode(...))</script>"

The payload was executed when an administrator viewed the Visitors page:

http://offsecwp/wp-admin/admin.php?page=visitors-app

### Result

A new administrator account was created:

* Username: zdnet
* Password: (created via payload)
* Role: Administrator

### Payload Logic

The JavaScript payload:

* Requested `/wp-admin/user-new.php`
* Extracted a nonce value
* Submitted a POST request to create a new admin user

